wkhtmltopdf 0.13.0 - Debian Package Files
=========================================

This directory contains the Debian packaging metadata for wkhtmltopdf 0.13.0.

STRUCTURE
---------
debian/
├── DEBIAN/
│   ├── control       - Package metadata (version, dependencies, description)
│   ├── postinst      - Post-installation script (runs ldconfig)
│   └── postrm        - Post-removal script (cleans up)
└── usr/
    └── share/
        └── doc/
            └── wkhtmltopdf/
                ├── copyright         - License information (LGPL-3)
                └── changelog.Debian.gz - Changelog in Debian format

BUILDING THE PACKAGE
--------------------
From the root directory, run:

    ./build-deb.sh

This will:
1. Create the package structure
2. Copy binaries and libraries
3. Generate metadata
4. Build wkhtmltopdf_0.13.0_<arch>.deb

INSTALLING THE PACKAGE
----------------------
    sudo dpkg -i wkhtmltopdf_0.13.0_amd64.deb
    sudo apt-get install -f  # Install missing dependencies

PACKAGE CONTENTS
----------------
The package installs:
- /usr/local/bin/wkhtmltopdf      - Main binary
- /usr/local/bin/wkhtmltoimage    - Image converter binary
- /usr/local/lib/libwkhtmltox.so* - Shared library (with symlinks)
- /usr/local/include/wkhtmltox/   - C headers for library
- /etc/ld.so.conf.d/wkhtmltopdf.conf - ldconfig configuration

DEPENDENCIES
------------
See debian/DEBIAN/control for the full list.

Key dependencies:
- Qt5 libraries (Core, GUI, Network, SVG, XML Patterns)
- Qt WebEngine (recommended) or Qt WebKit (fallback)
- SSL, FontConfig, FreeType, X11 libraries

BACKEND SELECTION
-----------------
Version 0.13.0 features automatic backend detection:
- Qt WebEngine (Chromium) is used if available → Modern CSS3 support
- Qt WebKit is used as fallback → Legacy CSS support

No configuration needed! The best available backend is selected automatically.

VERSION HISTORY
---------------
0.13.0 (2024-11-09)
  - Automatic backend detection and selection
  - Full CSS3 support (Flexbox, Grid, Animations)
  - Multi-backend architecture
  - Improved installation and packaging
  - Comprehensive documentation

0.12.7-dev
  - Development version (previous)

